== 個人生活 ==
2008年，克羅格在卑詩省因為在素里超速被攔檢中的酒駕被起訴。<ref name="DUI"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/2008/04/01/nickelback_frontman_kroeger_convicted_of_dui.html|title=Nickelback frontman Kroeger convicted of DUI|accessdate=2014-10-07|date=2008-04-01|work=The Star|archive-date=2020-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924051003/https://www.thestar.com/entertainment/2008/04/01/nickelback_frontman_kroeger_convicted_of_dui.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

克羅格在2012年的7月1日開始與加拿大搖滾歌手[[艾薇兒|艾薇兒]]交往。<ref name="People2013">{{Cite web|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20713633,00.html|title=Avril Lavigne and Chad Kroeger Are Now Married (Really)|accessdate=2013-07-02|date=2013-07-02|work=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|first1=Kathy|last1=Ehrich Dowd|first2=Stephen M.|last2=Silverman|archive-date=2013-07-04|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6HrBS9FDZ?url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20713633,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>這段關係從她們在2012年三月之後的艾薇兒的第五張專輯中的寫作與錄音開始萌芽。<ref name="People2013"/>克羅格與艾薇兒在2012年8月文定。<ref name="laudadio">{{Cite web|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20623133,00.html|title=Avril Lavigne Engaged to Nickelback's Chad Kroeger|accessdate=2012-08-21|date=2012-08-21|last=Laudadio|first=Marisa|publisher=People|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.people.com%2Fpeople%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C20623133%2C00.html&date=2013-04-18|archivedate=2013-04-18|deadurl=yes}}</ref>這對伴侶在2013年的7月1日在法國結婚，而當天也是[[加拿大日|加拿大日]]。<ref name="People2013"/>艾薇兒與克羅格的蜜月在義大利的飛諾港。2014年9月，娛樂傳媒開始報導艾薇兒與克羅格在結婚後的一年就分居了。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/avril-lavigne-chad-kroeger-headed-for-a-split--2014179|title=Avril Lavigne, Chad Kroeger Headed For a Split  – Us Weekly|date=2014-09-17|work=usmagazine.com|access-date=2016-03-08|archive-date=2021-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306122323/https://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/avril-lavigne-chad-kroeger-headed-for-a-split--2014179/|dead-url=no}}</ref>當八卦持續圍繞在艾薇兒與克羅格目睹他們未戴婚戒時，在2014年尾提出了非正式的聲明。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2816659/Avril-Lavigne-Chad-Kroeger-deciding-split-good-claims-new-report.html|title=Avril Lavigne and Chad Kroeger 'deciding whether to split for good' – Daily Mail Online|work=Mail Online|access-date=2016-03-08|archive-date=2017-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170504083758/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2816659/Avril-Lavigne-Chad-Kroeger-deciding-split-good-claims-new-report.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>克羅格否認了這些有關分居以及滑稽的傳言。<ref>[http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6312148/chad-kroeger-avril-lavigne-marriage-rumors Chad Kroeger Finds Avril Lavigne Marriage Rumors 'Amusing'] {{Wayback|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6312148/chad-kroeger-avril-lavigne-marriage-rumors |date=20201114182442 }} November 8, 2014</ref>2015年9月2日，艾薇兒宣布她們在Instagram的帳戶分開。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://instagram.com/p/7I5TTpo4M0/|title=It is with heavy heart that Chad and I announce our separation today. Through not only the marriage, but the music as well, we've created many unforgettable moments. We are still, and forever will be, the best of friends, and will always care deeply for each other. To all our family, friends and fans, thank you sincerely for the support.|accessdate=2015-09-02|publisher=Instagram|archive-url=https://archive.today/20150905061435/https://instagram.com/p/7I5TTpo4M0/|archive-date=2015-09-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

